
# Landing Page

##  Project Overview
This project is a modern responsive landing page built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.  
It demonstrates page structure, responsive layouts, animations, and UI design.

##  Features
- Responsive design for mobile, tablet, and desktop
- Navigation menu with toggle button
- Smooth animations using GSAP and AOS
- Hero section with call-to-action buttons
- Clean typography and layout system

##  Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (DOM manipulation)
- GSAP Animation Library
- AOS (Animate on Scroll)

##  Project Structure
index.html
css/style.css
js/script.js
img/

##  How to Run
1. Download or clone the repository
2. Open `index.html` in your browser

